N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8151.01 - City of Kingston

State Regulations
(a) Broadway. The northbound and southbound roadways of Broadway between Route 587 and

Cornell Street in the City of Kingston. (b) Cornell Street. The northbound and
southbound roadways of Cornell Street between Broadway and Ten Broeck Avenue in
the City of Kingston. (c) Ten

Broeck Avenue. The eastbound and westbound roadways of Ten Broeck Avenue
between Cornell Street and the Roadway Express terminal. Notes
